## No Erlang distribution — all admin ops go through the Unix socket API.
## This avoids exposing epmd/distribution ports on a firewall box.
## To enable remote console, uncomment and set a strong random cookie:
##
##   -sname erlkoenig_nft
##   -setcookie <run: openssl rand -base64 32>
##   -kernel inet_dist_use_interface {127,0,0,1}
##   -start_epmd false

+sbwt very_short
